<h3>How to Clone and Rehost This Site</h3>

<h4>Download the Data</h4>

<p>
	Download the posts, replies, images, votes, and public profiles as a zip file.
</p>

<p>
	The data format allows for re-validation of the data integrity
	(similar to a blockchain) as well as rebuilding a complete copy
	of the site, either locally or online.
</p>

<p>
	The user accounts are owned and controlled by the users themselves
	using a private key, so the same account can be used across different
	clones. They are not included.
</p>

<h4>How to Create a Clone</h4>

<p>
	To create a clone, you will need to know how to do these things:
</p>

<pre>
1. Extract files to server or local computer

2. Run import script 

3. Run web server

4. Test it out to ensure it works

5. Keep an eye on the server to keep everything is OK.
</pre>